text: <!channel>: Happy Monday everyone! At 1pm today we will have a new coffee set-up installed in the kitchen! We will be getting a commercial sized coffee brewer that brews directly into airpots so we will have a much larger volume of coffee per pot. There will be some drilling noise for a few minutes, and the install will take approximately 90 minutes.
